Locating/Verifying/Assessing Email Addresses
https://hunter.io/email-finder - find email by name
https://hunter.io/domain-search - find email by domain
https://hunter.io/email-verifier - verify legitimacy of an email

https://tools.emailhippo.com/ - verify legitimacy of an email
https://tools.emailhippo.com/Apps/Disposable_Email_Address_Detector - check if an email is a DEA (Disposable Email Address)
https://tools.emailhippo.com/Apps/Email_Extractor - automatically extract email addresses from a text
https://tools.emailhippo.com/Apps/Domain-Age-Checker - check age of a domain (extracted from WHOIS)

https://email-checker.net/ - verify legitimacy of an email
